UID:cBQQJez97PXPT-EfROwfL
SUMMARY:Maple Wood Playfield: Land & Community Tending
DTSTAMP:20260327T031552Z
DTSTART:20260328T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Maple Wood Playfield. \
	\nENGAGEMENT 2 — URGENCY\\\, DECAY & CARE\\nYou’re invited to a community 
	land gathering held in gentleness\\\, intention\\\, and shared responsibil
	ity.\\nTogether\\\, we’ll tend the land through composting\\\, mulching\\\
	, soil repair\\\, and blackberry and laurel management — practicing care w
	ithout force and action without harm.\\nThese gatherings are a return to l
	and\\\, to care\\\, and to being in right relationship.\\nThis season\\\, 
	we continue nurturing the pocket food forest\\\, supporting a space of lea
	rning\\\, play\\\, and community care for young people and families. \\nAl
	ongside the land work\\\, we continue an optional book-and-film braid in p
	artnership with The Seattle Public Library Foundation. \\nReading Threads 
	(optional)\\n📖 M Archive — Alexis Pauline Gumbs\\n• Fire → Archive of Sky 
	— What We Became\\n• Dirt (Revisited)\\n📖 Hospicing Modernity — Vanessa Ma
	chado de Oliveira\\n• Faster Than Thought\\n• Living and Dying Well\\n• Su
	rrendering Arrogance \\nArt / Somatic Practices (optional)\\nBreath tracki
	ng during labor\\nOne-sentence writing (only what is necessary)\\nCome to 
	work. Come to observe. Come to rest.\\nAll forms of participation are welc
	ome. \\nTools\\\, gloves\\\, and snacks provided. No experience needed. \\
	n📍 Meet near the playground \\nRegister\n\nhttps://www.seattleparksfoundat
	ion.org/event/maple-playfield-land-community-tending-2/\n\nFrom The Seattl
	e Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/maple-playfield-land-commu
	nity-tending-2/
LOCATION:WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-parks-foundation
CATEGORIES:The Seattle Parks Foundation
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
END:VEVENT
