UID:gA6zKoqiCH0lGeNI8MAyA
SUMMARY:Kubota forest work - always ivy!
DTSTAMP:20260327T031553Z
DTSTART:20260404T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Kubota Garden.\\nSo muc
	h ivy! Every month\\\, volunteers make a big difference by removing ivy so
	 that trees\\\, bushes\\\, ferns and other native plants have room to grow
	. As you will quickly see\\\, the ivy covers large areas of ground and is 
	climbing up trees. We also are discovering small Himalayan blackberry plan
	ts and getting those out immediately is a priority. No experience is neede
	d – just bring your energy and interest in making a difference! We like to
	 show our thanks with homemade cookies at the end. \\nRegister\n\nhttps://
	www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/kubota-forest-work-always-ivy-2/\n\nF
	rom The Seattle Parks Foundation
